KissMangaPlusPlus (a Greasemonkey script)

=============

Add shortcut keys for easy navigating on KissManga

Shortcut List:

J/K		Next/Previous chapter
H		Go to Homepage
L		Go to Bookmark List
S		Search by Series Name
A		Search by Author/Artist
C		Go to Comment section
T		Go to top
B		Bookmark/Unbookmark a manga (Only works in Manga information page)

=============

Easy link for install
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/gerads/KissMangaPlusPlus/master/kissmangaplusplus.user.js

=============

Since the original project was last updated 2 years ago, I decided to fork my own version to include features and fixes I think are useful.

If the original author wants me to take it down, just let me know.
